## ğŸ“¦ Deploying to Vercel

### 1. Push to GitHub
```bash
git init
git remote add origin https://github.com/yourusername/weld-recruiting.git
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git push -u origin main
```

### 2. Deploy on [https://vercel.com](https://vercel.com)
- Click **New Project**
- Select your GitHub repo
- Add the `OPENAI_API_KEY` under Environment Variables
- Click **Deploy**

